@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_urvbfk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = (tmp * 0.18)
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v0 + 0.28) + tmp))
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.10 * v1 + 0.11) - 0.53) * wp.sin((v2 + 0.53 + v0 + 0.20)))
    v0 = wp.cos(v2)
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.32) - v1) / wp.exp(v0))
    tmp = (0.57 * wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.72)))
    tmp = 0.30
    data[tid] = v0
